==English==
===Noun===
'''[[carbon]] [[dioxide]]''' {{uncountable}}
{{wikipedia}}
#{{chemistry}} The normal [[oxide]] of [[carbon]], CO<sub>2</sub>; a [[colorless]], [[odorless]] [[gas]] formed during [[respiration]] and [[combustion]] and [[consumed]] by [[plant]]s during [[photosynthesis]].

====Derived terms====
*[[carbon dioxide snow]]

====Related terms====
